---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Services &mdash; Forge T Labs"
  description="Forge T Labs services across Dynamics 365, Modern Work, Azure and custom development."
  canonical=""
  ogType="website"
  active="Services"
>
<main id="top">
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; Services</div>
    <h1>What we <em>do</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Forge T Labs delivers AI cloud solutions on the Microsoft platform across four disciplines. Each one stands alone &mdash; together they cover the full Microsoft Cloud estate, from one accountable partner.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="mono">Our services</span>
      <h2>Four disciplines, <em>one</em> Microsoft partner.</h2>
      <p>From your first workshop to managed operations, we cover Dynamics 365, Microsoft 365,
        Azure and custom development &mdash; so you are not stitching together three vendors.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pillars">
      <article class="pillar reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7" rx="1.5"/></svg></div>
        <span class="num">Business applications</span>
        <h3>Dynamics 365</h3>
        <p>Sales, Customer Service, Field Service and Business Central &mdash; implemented, integrated and supported.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:18px">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/dynamics-365" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Explore Dynamics 365 &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="pillar reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M7 18a4 4 0 0 1 0-8 5.5 5.5 0 0 1 10.6-1.5A3.8 3.8 0 0 1 18 18H7Z"/></svg></div>
        <span class="num">Microsoft 365</span>
        <h3>Modern Work</h3>
        <p>Secure, productive Microsoft 365 workplaces &mdash; migration, Teams, SharePoint, security and adoption.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:18px">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/modern-work" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Explore Modern Work &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="pillar reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><path d="M12 3v6m0 6v6M3 12h6m6 0h6" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg></div>
        <span class="num">Cloud &amp; intelligence</span>
        <h3>Azure &amp; AI</h3>
        <p>Cloud infrastructure and applied AI &mdash; landing zones, migration, Copilot and custom AI solutions.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:18px">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/azure-ai" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Explore Azure &amp; AI &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="pillar reveal">
        <div class="ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3fc878" stroke-width="1.6"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3.2"/><path d="M12 2v3m0 14v3M2 12h3m14 0h3M5 5l2 2m10 10l2 2M5 19l2-2M17 7l2-2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></div>
        <span class="num">Built for you</span>
        <h3>Custom Solutions</h3>
        <p>Bespoke applications on the Power Platform and Azure &mdash; including our own ISV products.</p>
        <div style="margin-top:18px">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/custom-solutions" style="width:100%;justify-content:center">Explore Custom Solutions &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="band">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head reveal">
      <span class="mono">How we engage</span>
      <h2>A consistent method, <em>whichever service you need</em>.</h2>
      <p>Every engagement runs the same disciplined four-stage path.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="sn">STAGE 01</div>
        <h4>Discover</h4><p>Workshops to capture requirements, map your data and define a clear scope.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="sn">STAGE 02</div>
        <h4>Architect</h4><p>A Well-Architected design across security, identity, integration and AI.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="sn">STAGE 03</div>
        <h4>Build</h4><p>Iterative delivery with regular demos and tight feedback loops.</p></div>
      <div class="step reveal"><div class="sn">STAGE 04</div>
        <h4>Operate</h4><p>Go-live support, adoption and managed services that keep improving.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cta-band reveal">
      <div class="glow"></div>
      <h2>Let's scope your project.</h2>
      <p>Tell us what you are trying to achieve on the Microsoft Cloud and we will bring the
        right mix of these services to get you there.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Book a discovery call &rarr;</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/industries">Industries we serve</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
